        public T withListColumn(ParquetColumnWriterOptions.ParquetListColumnWriterOptions child)
        Set the list column meta. Lists should have only one child in ColumnVector, but the metadata expects a LIST column to have two children and the first child to be the ParquetColumnWriterOptions.DUMMY_CHILD. This is the current behavior in cudf and will change in future
